---
title: Portuguese-Style Grilled Chicken with Potatoes and Salad
description: Grilled chicken gets a classic Portuguese treatment in this recipe! Warming paprika- and cumin-marinated chicken breasts are a match made in heaven for steamy, garlicky potatoes and a bright, fresh salad. Tonight, the best churrasqueira is in your backyard!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-grille-a-la-portugaise-eacdfb81.jpg
